name: 200 Soy Tea Lights, Unscented, Dye Free, Clear Cups, Vegan
description:
200 Soy tea lights, Unscented, dye free, by CrystalgardenCandles on Etsy.
This posting is for 200 soy tea lights. Soy wax is a clean burning product, that is renewable and healthier than paraffin wax, which is made from fossil fuels. 
These tea lights are dye free and unscented and as always - filled to the top!!! Ready to use for your tart or potpourri burner or just for decoration at home or at a wedding or party. These tea-lights come in clear pastic tea light cups with lead free cotton wicks. Each tea light burns approximately six + hours. These are great for weddings.

The tea lights come in cello bags with label.



Please contact me for shipping rates outside the United States.

Thank you so much for looking! 

CrystalgardenCandles

name: 40 Soy Votive Candles, Unscented, Dye Free, Vegan
description:
These soy votive candles are unscented and dye free. Handmade by CrystalgardenCandles.
These votive candles are made with 100 % natural, Vegan soy wax. They are unscented and dye free, which makes them perfect for weddings and parties or people who are allergic to the fragrances. Each votive burns approximately 15 hours. They have a creamy white appearance.
The price is for unscented votive candles only. If you need a larger quantity let me know and I will make a special posting for you!
If you have any special requests, don't hesitate to contact me. I will be happy to assist you!

Please contact me for shipping rates outside the United States.

Thank you so much for looking!
